text: Motion
Motion
Yaaay~! The training camp is over~~~!
Ah, it was such a great training camp, wasn't it?

Mmm~
Hinana, you really worked hard, didn't you~?

Yeah,
I think you did a great job.
And you also had to endure something, right?"

Oh~? 
What do you mean~?

The cream puff thing.
In the end, we couldn't get it.

Aha~ 
Bringing up that topic again~?

Producer, did you really want to eat that
with Hinana that badly~?
Haha... Yeah, maybe I did.

I thought it could be like a reward for
choosing the training camp and working hard.

But in the end,
maybe I just wanted to eat it with Hinana!

Right~...
Well then, I have really good news for you, Producer~!

About that cream puff...
Hinana asked Mom to buy it for us~!
There's also one for Producer~"
Eh...! I-Is that so...?

Yeah~! Because you worked really hard during the
training camp, you deserve a reward, right?
Both Hinana and Producer do!
